videos.headline: Allgeier rushes 34 yards for BYU's first TD
videos.description: Tyler Allgeier keeps it it close to the sideline, but stays inbounds and dives into the end zone for a 34-yard touchdown run to put BYU on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Allgeier rushes 34 yards for BYU's first TD) 2020/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Katoa scores again for BYU
videos.description: Zach Wilson tosses it over the defender to a wide-open Lopini Katoa who takes it in for the 15-yard BYU touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Katoa scores again for BYU) 2020/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Katoa lunges for his third TD
videos.description: Lopini Katoa keeps moving his feet and just crosses the plane for his third score of the game for BYU.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Katoa lunges for his third TD) 2020/09/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Romney breaks four tackles and scores
videos.description: Zach Wilson lobs it to Gunner Romney, who gets free from defenders and scores the 45-yard touchdown.
